12.24	Michael_Stivic	Michael Stivic	Michael Casimir Stivic is a fictional character on the long running American television sitcom of the 1970s, All in the Family. He was the live-in son-in-law of the series's lead character, the bigoted and undereducated Archie Bunker, who frequently called him "Meathead". Michael was the husband of Archie's daughter Gloria (played by Sally Struthers). Rob Reiner (son of comedian Carl Reiner) played the role of Michael Stivic throughout the series.	
